  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is an immersive first-person single-player horror game. Players will take on the role of an ordinary person returning home late at night, who inexplicably steps into a special space on a familiar path. You must explore and move forward in this space filled with unknown fears.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game is divided into four chapters. Players will explore four distinctly different styled areas in sequence. Please be advised that some scenes contain bloody elements, and players should mentally prepare themselves accordingly.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/207726849a9c4db0f4341329b07a2c1a.poster.avif?t=1746026634\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/207726849a9c4db0f4341329b07a2c1a.webm?t=1746026634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/207726849a9c4db0f4341329b07a2c1a.mp4?t=1746026634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/a43c1d9fd6cba10ec530720c5defe1f0.poster.avif?t=1746026634\" width=384 height=216 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/a43c1d9fd6cba10ec530720c5defe1f0.webm?t=1746026634\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3564570/extras/a43c1d9fd6cba10ec530720c5defe1f0.mp4?t=1746026634\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=